### Create tenant
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Serenity Spa", "email": "owner@serenity.example", "website": "https://serenity.example" }

### Ingest fixture
POST http://localhost:3000/api/kb/ingest?tenantId={{TENANT_ID}}

### Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/kb/search?q=opening%20hours&tenantId={{TENANT_ID}}

### WhatsApp inbound – FAQ
POST http://localhost:3000/api/channels/wa/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenantId": "{{TENANT_ID}}", "from": "+971500000000", "text": "What are your opening hours?" }

### WhatsApp inbound – Booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/channels/wa/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenantId": "{{TENANT_ID}}", "from": "+971500000001", "text": "I'd like a 60m massage tomorrow after 3pm" }

### WhatsApp inbound – Payment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/channels/wa/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenantId": "{{TENANT_ID}}", "from": "+971500000002", "text": "Can I pay a deposit now?" }

### Invoice send
POST http://localhost:3000/api/invoices/{{INVOICE_ID}}/send

### Invoice mark paid
POST http://localhost:3000/api/invoices/{{INVOICE_ID}}/mark-paid
